{"tid":967771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍將首次在沖繩實施「反艦飛彈演習」　回應解放軍通過宮古海峽","createTime":"2019-01-03T18:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T23:44:41.000Z","uid":35790,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dd3ea9128ca395623631cf50442f3e8299f88c7d","tid":967771,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T18:35:03.000Z","msg":"美軍將首次在沖繩實施「反艦飛彈演習」　回應解放軍通過宮古海峽<br />\n<br />\n美軍為了回應中國軍力崛起後，多次以戰機、戰艦通過宮古海峽與其他沖繩周邊海域的舉動，將於今年首度在沖繩實施「反艦飛彈」演習。<br />\n<br />\n根據日媒《產經新聞》報導，美軍已經通知日本自衛隊，計畫在戰略地位重要的沖繩部署陸基反艦飛彈，作為對中國回應的有效措施，並且希望自衛隊能夠調動地面部隊參與相關的演習，加強與美軍的聯合應對能力。<br />\n<br />\n《產經新聞》進一步指出，美軍將部署的是M142高機動性多管火箭系統（HIMARS）是一款安裝在中型戰術車輛的多管火箭，並搭載ATACMS戰術飛彈，可在300公里的射程內執行反艦任務。<br />\n<br />\n《產經新聞》分析，中國航空母艦遼寧號，28年來首次在沖繩島與宮古島之間穿越，完成了第一次處入西太平洋的任務，同時還開發出被稱為是「航母殺手」的東風-21D反艦彈道飛彈，加大了對東海周邊的控制。<br />\n<br />\n專家指出，中國日益增加的海上活動，是打算控制所謂「第一島鏈」計畫的一環。第一島鏈包含沖繩、台灣及菲律賓。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190103/1347358.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190103%2F1347358.htm&d=NGDs88IILeUySPzm2k3Y13Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=1eb9cdfe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190103/1347358.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8af9c80a0e80376d335a9281310091392afcfa28","tid":967771,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T18:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a4a820434d6332b4466d2c1345f583afb74b38","tid":967771,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T23:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f015d66ba9d1bf15ed3b26bc4d5ee1fce5ad95","tid":967771,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T23:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72920ea3fa0776213e6b35f1a771ea9b7fb0f03","tid":967771,"uid":5420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T23:29:14.000Z","msg":"咩叫實施演習<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f810b314f69c0881953f2d91a4002603acaa795","tid":967771,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T23:40:28.000Z","msg":"有生之年應該可以見證到第二次北洋艦隊全滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46f25ba0d8abc367882e93c9bb803d86c0b4ebb","tid":967771,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T23:44:41.000Z","msg":"美國的「陸軍戰術飛彈系統」（ATACMS)可以說是世界上最先進的地對地戰術彈道飛彈"}]}